Start
/ Test: POST with JSON body, verify response
- set %body% to { "name": "Alice", "age": 30 }
- post https://httpbin.org/post, %body%, unsigned, write to %response%
- if %response% is not empty then
    - write out 'POST request returned data'
- if %response.StatusCode% equals 200 then
    - write out 'Status code is 200'
